HEADWORD: Collineation
<hw>Col*lin`e*a"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>collineare</ets> to direct in a straight line. See
<er>Collimation</er>.]</ety> <def>The act of aiming at, or directing in
a line with, a fixed object.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark>
<rj><au>Johnson.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

